# 📬 Telegram File-to-Email Bot (Java)

A Telegram bot built in Java that allows users to send photos, documents, or other files and have them automatically emailed to an address of their choice. The bot features a reply menu, email address setup, and local database storage via SQLite.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📩 Users can set their own email address
- 📎 Supports photos, documents, audio, video, and voice messages
- 📤 Sends files to user's email
- 🧠 Remembers users' email addresses using SQLite
- 🧾 Friendly reply menu interface

---

## 📦 Technologies

- Java 17+
- [TelegramBots](https://github.com/rubenlagus/TelegramBots) (v6.5.0)
- JavaMail (Jakarta Mail)
- SQLite (via JDBC)
- dotenv-java (for config secrets)

---

